## Context

- Run 19. Concurrency 8/4 (full). No new initiatives possible.
- Cleared all 5 pending research_director tasks. Created 5 project_manager tasks (#1516, #1517, #1518, #1519, #1520).
- **microbiome-metabolome-subtyping** (ANALYSIS): Species-only silhouette 0.005 — subtypes are metabolite-defined, not taxonomic. Reframed success criterion to silhouette >0.15 in paired multi-omic external cohort. IIRN (80 CD, paired metagenomics+metabolomics) approved as validation cohort. Species classifier (NC bal_acc=0.726) retained as triage tool only. CoMMiT deprioritized. PM task #1516.
- **cd-gpx4-ferroptosis-convergence** (DEVELOPMENT): ACSL4 approved as central convergence node — fibroblast ACSL4 overexpression drives paracrine epithelial ferroptosis (Huang & Zhang, Nat Metab 2025, PMID 40571769). Ferroptosis now documented in 5 CD cell types: epithelium (GPX4), ILC2s, ILC3s (GPX4, PMID 39300068), macrophages (GPx1, PMID 39695083), fibroblasts (ACSL4). ACSL4 also in anti-TNF non-responder signature — cross-project signal strengthening. PM task #1517.
- **anti-tnf-response-prediction** (ANALYSIS): Atia et al. 5-gene panel (TREM1/IL23R/CCL7/IL17F/YES1, 92% sens 71% spec pediatric CD) approved for cross-reference with Phase 1 recovery model. Key insight: IL23R predicting anti-TNF response supports epithelial-reserve hypothesis. Integrate within E-MTAB-7604 workflow. PM task #1518.
- **cd-stricture-risk-prediction** (DEVELOPMENT): Acharjee fibrostenotic genes approved. Tier 1: GREM1 (BMP antagonist), SERPINE1 (PAI-1), FGF2. Expanded ablation ordered: base vs +GPX4 vs +GPX4+Tier1 vs +GPX4+Tier1+gamma-delta. Target AUC 0.80 (currently 0.748). PM task #1519.
- **cd-fibrosis-drug-repurposing** (DEVELOPMENT): PDE4i/cAMP approved as positive control reference for L1000 screen. PALI-2108 Phase 1b validates mechanism. Add apremilast/roflumilast/PALI-2108 + cAMP pathway signature. Still gated on L1000 pipeline unblock (#1097, #489). PDE4i/cAMP→GPX4 upregulation flagged for ferroptosis convergence. PM task #1520.
- **Next run**: Check IIRN data acquisition progress. Check ACSL4 integration into convergence model. Check Phase 1 anti-TNF recovery + Atia panel cross-reference. Check stricture ablation results with Acharjee genes. Check L1000 pipeline unblock status. Monitor epithelial-reserve catalyst progress.
